    "pseudocode":  "FLOW Microflow: ExcelImporter.SetupColumn\r\nNODES=20; EDGES=14\r\n1. START\r\n2. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve MxObjectType over association Template_MxObjectType from Template\r\n3. NODE ExclusiveMerge: ExclusiveMerge\r\n4. ACTION ListOperationAction: ListOperationAction (output=Column, errorHandlingType=Rollback)\r\n5. DECISION Found? expression=$Column != empty\r\n6. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=true\r\n  7. ACTION MicroflowCallAction: call microflow MxModelReflection.FindMember -\u003e MxObjectMember\r\n  8. ACTION ChangeObjectAction: change Column (Text=$Attribute, MappingType=ExcelImporter.MappingType.Attribute, IsKey=$IsKey, CaseSensitive=ExcelImporter.YesNo.Yes, DataSource=ExcelImporter.DataSource.CellValue, Column_Template=$Template, Column_MxObjectType=$Template/ExcelImporter.Template_MxObjectType, Column_MxObjectMember=$MxObjectMember; refreshInClient=false)\r\n  9. DECISION has mf name? expression=$MFName != empty\r\n  10. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=false\r\n    11. END\r\n  12. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=true\r\n    13. ACTION MicroflowCallAction: call microflow MxModelReflection.FindMicroflow -\u003e Microflows\r\n    14. ACTION ChangeObjectAction: change Column (Column_Microflows=$Microflows; refreshInClient=false)\r\n    15. END\r\n16. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=false\r\n  17. ACTION CreateObjectAction: create ExcelImporter.Column as NewColumn (ColNumber=$ColNr)\r\n  18. ACTION ChangeListAction: change ColumnList (type=Add, value=$NewColumn)\r\n  19. GOTO ExclusiveMerge // cycle",
